ound nutmeg.","Long skewers can be cut to fit the Varoma tray.","For a stronger flavour marinate the chicken in <b>step 2<b> for a few hours or overnight.","For a vegetarian version of this dish, replace chicken with halloumi cheese, cut in cubes (2 cm). Follow the recipe excluding the extra cooking time in <b>step 7.<b>","For a spicier dish add <b>½-1 tsp<b> of chilli sauce to the marinade ingredients."],"basicInfo":["medium","35m","2h","4 portions"]}